    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《to a T》是一款叙事冒险游戏，讲述了一名身体呈T字形的13岁少年的非凡人生。少年生活在一个普通的海边小镇，可以步行、乘坐火车，甚至骑着自己最爱的独轮车四处探索，并与镇上的有趣居民们互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/cf86f46596830e2fe716d3a0838b5052.poster.avif?t=1749748161\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/cf86f46596830e2fe716d3a0838b5052.webm?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/cf86f46596830e2fe716d3a0838b5052.mp4?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从这名少年忠实的毛茸茸小狗伙伴和慈爱的母亲，到一群可气的恶霸，还有一头能做出超美味三明治的长颈鹿，小镇上的角色各具特色。一次偶然的邂逅之后，少年发现了自己新觉醒的能力，而一段围绕从天而降、被光芒包裹的神秘物体展开的故事也由此拉开序幕。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/a3095095d848384bf055cb5af248f74d.poster.avif?t=1749748161\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/a3095095d848384bf055cb5af248f74d.webm?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/a3095095d848384bf055cb5af248f74d.mp4?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>特色：</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >章节式故事：在一个于数日内逐渐展开的故事中，和Teen一起寻找融入他人之道，并发现全新的自我。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小游戏：操控Teen应对日常生活中的各种不同场景。控制Teen的手臂触碰物体并与之互动。让Teen张开嘴巴来吃东西或喝水。从抚摸小狗到享用早餐，即便方式独特，Teen依然能完成许多事情。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索小镇：除了主线故事外，还可以收集硬币、寻找美丽的观景点、逛遍全镇的商店，或在自由模式下四处走动，与有趣的角色交流。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色自定义：以你喜欢的风格打扮Teen。在镇上的商店购买新衣服，丰富衣柜，尝试各种有趣的穿搭组合。一只非常可爱的小狗。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/e5d5c163d20e3412e7d004cc26daa408.poster.avif?t=1749748161\" width=616 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/e5d5c163d20e3412e7d004cc26daa408.webm?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1875320/extras/e5d5c163d20e3412e7d004cc26daa408.mp4?t=1749748161\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
